com.github.wuic.resource.impl
Class AbstractWuicResource

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.resource.impl.AbstractWuicResource
All Implemented Interfaces:
WuicResource, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ByteArrayWuicResource, FilePathWuicResource, HttpWuicResource
public abstract class AbstractWuicResource
extends Object
implements WuicResource

Base implementation of the WuicResource interface. A WuicResource is often represented by a name and a FileType. This class already manages it.

0.3.0
